{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_helage_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_helage_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"命途","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_helage_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["临光","罗德岛干员","？？？","赫拉格","萨卡兹雇佣兵A","萨卡兹雇佣兵B","爱国者","阿米娅","萨卡兹雇佣兵","整合运动A","整合运动B","整合运动成员","盾卫"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"个人剧情 赫拉格","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_bg_bg_bridge.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......","id":10,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_char_148_nearl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......我们已经站了多久了？","id":12,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"核心城......都几乎看不见了。","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......你的伤还没痊愈，去休息吧，这里有我就好。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"不，我不是这个意思，就，怎么讲，你明白的......","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"希望阿米娅他们能早点回来......","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"嗯。","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","id":21},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":22},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"担心领袖的心是好的，这是罗德岛向心力的证明。但是否要勉强自己，又是另一码事。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你甚至都站不稳了，年轻人。别对你的同伴隐瞒伤势，我看得一清二楚。","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"啊？你......赫拉格先生？","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"赫拉格先生说得对，我们迟早会需要你的，但不是现在。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_char_148_nearl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"养好伤之后，我们再并肩作战。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_char_148_nearl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......嘿。我一个无名小卒，凭什么能和耀骑士并肩作战，这可太抬举我啦。","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"——不过，赫拉格先生，现在情况特殊，您还是该待在舰内的......","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"这我当然明白。奈音和其他孩子还在接受检查，等结束后我自会去安顿好他们。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"如果是这样的话......好吧，真要有什么情况，带我这个伤员，也只会拖后腿吧。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"那我先撤了，二位保重。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":42},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":43},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"300","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":44},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":45},{"type":"dialog","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":47},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.6","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"开阔的视野，从这里可以眺望到那座失控的城市。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#6","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您的视力很好。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_char_148_nearl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1#2","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#6","focus":"1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"向来如此。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_char_188_helage_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你们掩护数支小队登上了切尔诺伯格，可我从那位医生的口中听到的是一个无畏的计划。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_char_188_helage_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#6","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"但在战场上，无畏、勇猛、坚决，这些难能可贵的品质往往伴随着牺牲。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"无畏并非无谋。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"我起先没有料到，你们会是这样的战士。","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......利用沙暴和光线作掩护，即使是训练有素的士兵，也很难保证这种异想天开的突袭能够成功，值得赞叹。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"赫拉格先生，我听说Scout先生最后的遗物，是经由你手回到了罗德岛。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你想说，这是罗德岛普遍的品性？","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"我不能如此断论。我想每一位干员，哪怕是我，与Scout先生所抱有的觉悟都有区别。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"但每一位干员——此时此刻，愿意为感染者，为罗德岛而战的每一个人，都不会畏惧战斗。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"人总是为了不同的理由而战。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......所以当他们被许以一个过于宏大，甚至能吻合一切诉求的壮美愿景时，他们会迷失在洪流里。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"2","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您是说整合运动？","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_char_148_nearl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"1","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......都是一样的。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"赫拉格先生，前往那座城的干员们，都心怀信念，不曾动摇片刻。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"我选择相信那个信念，他们的信念。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"这是罗德岛干员的义务，以及，感谢您愿意费力带回Scout先生最后的通讯设备，当时切尔诺伯格的局势应该十分凶险。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......可惜，我与那位战士未曾谋面。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他的牺牲足以让战士动容。这使我相信他的意志至今仍有迹可循。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"但“牺牲”一词并非往事，眼下这场仗，罗德岛还会牺牲许多，甚至更多。","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"比起牺牲，我们更该在意牺牲换来的是什么。","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"而我的职责仅仅是在此处守望，等待他们的流血与奋斗换回正义的成果。","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......我曾见过不少像你这样的卡西米尔人，年轻的骑士，但他们多有缺失。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"我听那些干员称呼你为耀骑士，你先前的表现的确令人印象深刻——","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"——据我所知，在如今的卡西米尔，只持一字封号的骑士，无一例外都是他们之中的佼佼者，你为何离开了故土？","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"2","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"在如今的卡西米尔，骑士的含义也大不相同。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_char_148_nearl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您也离开了乌萨斯，这是您说的，每个人都为不同的理由而战。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"年轻的耀骑士，你叫什么名字？","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"玛嘉烈·临光。或者，干员代号，临光。","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......所以......他们称你为“临光”。","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":102},{"type":"dialog","id":103},{"type":"character","id":104},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":105},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_exciting02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":108,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":109},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵A","text":"W在哪儿！？这种时候——她为什么不在这里！？","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_054","focus":"2","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"......现在你还指望她？加尔森怎么死的，我们都心知肚明不是吗？","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_054","focus":"1","id":114},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵A","text":"你——","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_054","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"别废话！W也好，塔露拉也好，天知道她们在想什么。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"我们都是拿钱卖命的，对吧，别被这些感染者影响了，他们要的是他们的未来，和我们没有半点关系！","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"把眼前的敌人干掉，然后，跟着活下去的那一方继续走，这就是我的方针！","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"现在，告诉我，W联络不上，塔露拉弃置了我们，在这两个人，随便谁，再次给我们一个命令之前，告诉我，你们该听谁的！？","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":122},{"type":"character","id":123},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_bg_bg_cenbri.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":125},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":127},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_089","id":128},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"发生了什么？这些萨卡兹怎么都......","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_089.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"唔！","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_089.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"他们产生了混乱，我们乘机溜过去，快......别被发现......我们得按计划确保——","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_089.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"——！？","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_089.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"character","id":136},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":138},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":139},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":141},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":142},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":144},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你，不能。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_avg_npc_025_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":147},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_imp_blunt_h","id":148},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":149},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":150},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":153},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"？！","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"character","id":158},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_bg_bg_bridge.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":160},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":161},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":162,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"时至今日，我仍记得巴克莱那晚露出的表情。哪怕银枪的皮加索斯亲临战场一线，他也没露出过那股复杂神色。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他说，除了银枪的皮加索斯之外，我们又多了一个金色的对手。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"金色。金色的天马。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"一名刚崭露头角的军事统帅，在数小时内重组了本已经被突袭打散的众多骑士团，在那处峡谷，只靠血肉步卒据守了三月有余。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他让乌萨斯损失了远超预想的数字，使得集团军不得不调配高速军舰打破既定的阵型，也使得冬季行动不得不缩小规模。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"临光家族应该被卡西米尔奉为英雄。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"可是现在，继承了他血脉的年轻孩子......却被逐出了卡西米尔？","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"只是一些卑劣的往事......不值得赫拉格先生深究。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_char_148_nearl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"但无论我在大地何处，我仍以临光二字为豪。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你的祖父还好吗？","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"2","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......上一次与家乡联络，祖父已经卧病不起。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_char_148_nearl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"岁月......岁月总是出人意料。战争留下了英雄，也留下了创口。","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你痛恨乌萨斯吗？","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......我从未亲身经历战争，赫拉格先生。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"但我深知乌萨斯带去了许多场惨烈的战争，这个事实不会改变。而不少卡西米尔人也都痛恨乌萨斯人，哪怕，直到今日。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......否定这种痛恨，教那些在战争中失去了亲人与土地的人不去痛恨，这种行为近乎一种酷刑。","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您是一位军人......但我并非征战骑士。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你仍是个卡西米尔人。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"现在我也从未否认过这一点，我愿意为阿米娅倾诉的那个理想，为感染者而战——","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"——但也许迟早有一天，我还是会回到卡西米尔。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你还年轻，耀骑士。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"是的......你还年轻。你还有纠正自己和这一切的机会。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":199},{"type":"dialog","id":200},{"type":"character","id":201},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_bg_bg_graduate.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":203},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":205,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":206},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"这......这不可能......梅菲斯特他......他......","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"这是什么？异变？喂，你们还听得懂......唔......啊......","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"呃啊......啊......让......让他们......走......！","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":212},{"type":"character","id":213},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":215},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","id":217},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动A","text":"塔露拉背叛了我们！！","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_1","focus":"1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动B","text":"不可能！爱国者才是真正的叛徒！杀了他！他是个萨卡兹，是个温迪戈，还是个乌萨斯军人！他有什么可信任的！？","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":222},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":223},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵A","text":"啧。现在轮到我们站队了。","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_054","focus":"1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵A","text":"怎么说？W只留了个驻扎的命令就没影了，她是不是已经被塔露拉杀了？","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵A","text":"其他队伍......？","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_054","focus":"2","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"联系不上，现在那些感染者疯子已经开始围攻爱国者了——","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"——不过大部分人还在混乱，这就对了，他们又不是军人，这场变故比我听闻的任何一次政变都要突然——","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_054","focus":"1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵A","text":"去找爱国者的队伍汇合？","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_054","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"——萨卡兹宁愿跟着萨卡兹混，这不是铁律吗？","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵B","text":"再说，他可是博卓卡斯替啊。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_054.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":239},{"type":"dialog","id":240},{"type":"character","id":241},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_bg_bg_bridge.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":243},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":245,"musicid":4},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"切尔诺伯格。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"似乎它的脚步仍没有停下。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您在那生活了很久吗？","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"不算太久，很不幸，我的寿命比寻常乌萨斯人稍长一些。","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"但你说生活......我的确生活在那座城市里。","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你能想象吗？那曾经也是一座有游乐场、百货商店和人造湖泊公园的移动城市。","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"现在，核心城抛弃了那些被天灾摧毁的废城区，它轻易地把多少代人建立起来的东西抛弃了。","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"甚至连这座城市自己，都要为了一个可怕的阴谋捐躯。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"切尔诺伯格并不算美轮美奂，工厂污染了天空。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"但那里有多少无辜的乌萨斯人的生活，这些事情，那些发起阴谋的幕后黑手，有谁去想过？","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"谁都没有。","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"2","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"愤怒蒙蔽了他们。","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_char_148_nearl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"蒙蔽了所有人，我们都不例外。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"现在我看见的，那不是一座城市。是以无数人生活的毁灭作燃料，被野心驱动的暴力的机器。","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他们利用了所有人生存的意志。他们先是取走了感染者生存的权利，最后连他们的意志都要剥夺。","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"2","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您在那里的诊所......","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_char_148_nearl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......我所建立起的东西，被摧毁过太多次。只要奈音他们没事，废墟就只是砖瓦，还不是毁灭。","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"奈音他们没事，而罗德岛的确能提供治疗，这是我唯一欣慰的事情。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您把他们保护得很好，否则，在整合运动瘫痪城市后，从切尔诺伯格安全撤出近乎天方夜谭。","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"我只想保护好他们而已。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您甚至放弃了乌萨斯将领的身份。","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......是的，但乌萨斯的土地仍在追逐我。","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"而有时候，看着切尔诺伯格开动的时候，我曾分不清是乌萨斯在追逐我，还是在远离我。","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......您不愿与乌萨斯为敌。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1#3","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"乌萨斯——在它腐朽的身躯沉没在无止境的进军中之前，这片大地不该有任何人或事物与乌萨斯为敌。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"我曾将生命奉献给乌萨斯，战争是军人的天职，我只是履行了我信任过的职责。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"只是......只是时至今日，我已经走出了那片泥沼，得以从别的视角眺望我曾经生活过的地方——","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"——如同你一样，耀骑士。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"一个卡西米尔人、萨米人、龙门人，会如何看待历代陛下的指点对这片大地的深远影响？","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他们是如何看待与乌萨斯的战争的？","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"你说，你未曾经历战争。你还年轻，你还有回避这些问题的权利。但答案我们心知肚明。","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"战争没有答案，战争不需要答案。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"2","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......暴力改变不了任何事情。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_char_148_nearl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"是的......暴力。","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"先皇曾令乌萨斯荣耀，我们曾穷其一生为之奋斗的宏愿，如他所说，乌萨斯不过是他双手的延伸。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"可他是否真的有把乌萨斯所有的子民，看作乌萨斯的一部分？","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他会不会......","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":299},{"type":"character","id":300},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":301},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":302},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":303},{"type":"character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_1","id":304},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"爱国者死了！","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"那个乌萨斯的间谍死了！他不可信！塔露拉将带领感染者走向胜利！！","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_char_1002_nsabr_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"character","id":309},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":310},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":311},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":312},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"让塔露拉和她那些蠢笨的卫士明白，她屈服不了这里所有的意志！","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"让他们吠叫，让他们挣扎，叛徒都会被受奴役者之盾碾压而过，我们会连成山脉！","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"为了大尉！为了......爱国者！","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":318},{"type":"character","id":319},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":320},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":321},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":322},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":323},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"......爱国者......那个温迪戈？博卓卡斯替？","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"他......","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":327},{"type":"dialog","id":328},{"type":"character","id":329},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":330},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":331},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":334},{"type":"subtitle","text":"爱国者死了！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":335},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":336},{"type":"subtitle","text":"爱国者死了！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":337},{"type":"subtitle","id":338},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":339},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":340},{"type":"dialog","id":341},{"type":"character","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_bg_bg_bridge.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":344},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":346,"musicid":5},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1#3","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"1","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......等等。","id":348,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"那是，核心城的指挥塔......","id":349,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"它在燃烧。","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1#3","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......唔。","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"阿米娅......她们......","id":353,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"这只是一个开始。","id":355,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"整合运动的领袖不是个寻常感染者。她的实力谋略并非她最真实的一面，盘绕在整合运动背后的巨大阴影已经露出了獠牙。","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1#3","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"我们都得小心，当他们的奸计得逞，罗德岛，龙门，感染者，没有人能逃离一场新的洪流。","id":358,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1#3","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......不知道阿米娅面对的是什么样的敌人。","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#2","focus":"1","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"罗德岛的领袖，她比你更年轻。","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"整合运动煽动起的感染者暴徒，潜藏在其中的幕后黑手，又或者......","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......他们会直面爱国者。","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1","focus":"2","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"爱国者。","id":366,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_char_148_nearl_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_148_nearl_1","name2":"char_188_helage_1#3","focus":"2","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"复述他的名字吧，他名副其实——纯血的温迪戈，乌萨斯军人。","id":368,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"或者说，北原感染者游击队的领袖，博卓卡斯替。","id":369,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他会是拦在罗德岛与整合运动之间的最后一道壁垒。","id":370,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_char_188_helage_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1#3","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"2","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"......我在紧急临时会议上听闻过这个名字。我很少看见凯尔希医生如此谨慎对待一个敌人......一个敌人个体。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_char_148_nearl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......他当得上这份谨慎，有过之而无不及。","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"2","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"听上去，二位是旧识？","id":376,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_char_148_nearl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"我们曾是战友，而他是一个真正的战士。","id":378,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"与他的血统无关，与他的军功与身份都无关。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"——把温迪戈称作乌萨斯人，让你感到意外吗？","id":380,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"2","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"不。","id":382,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"身份和思想不应被出身决定，这一点我已经习以为常。","id":383,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您似乎觉得罗德岛胜算更小？","id":384,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_char_148_nearl_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#3","focus":"1","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......未必。","id":386,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"博卓卡斯替走不出他为自己划下的边界，为了他的理想，为了......他所相信的理想。","id":387,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"罗德岛为了实现自身目的而选择斩首塔露拉，这很莽撞，但也是实现一个折中结果的唯一办法。","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......但他不同。他挑起了那个象征着感染者与反抗者的形象，放任这个符号不断放大。","id":389,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"整合运动因他而有力，也会因此，成为他最大的软肋。","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"2","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"临光","text":"您是指？","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_char_148_nearl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","name2":"char_148_nearl_1#4","focus":"1","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":395},{"type":"dialog","id":396},{"type":"character","id":397},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_dignified_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":398,"musicid":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":399},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":400},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":402},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":403},{"type":"subtitle","text":"切尔诺伯格的指挥塔开始熊熊燃烧。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":404},{"type":"subtitle","text":"赫拉格远眺着被染成殷红的天空，久久没有收回视线。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":405},{"type":"subtitle","text":"那里是乌萨斯。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":406},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一座真真实实的城市。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":407},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一个逝去的幻影。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":408},{"type":"subtitle","id":409},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":410},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":411},{"type":"character","name":"char_188_helage_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":412},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"......","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"命运把他牵扯到了一个死局之中，他早有意识，但也绝不会屈服。","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他会战斗到底。","id":416,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫拉格","text":"他会迎来死亡。","id":417,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_char_188_helage_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":418},{"type":"character","id":419},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":420},{"type":"image","id":421}],"characters":["临光","罗德岛干员","？？？","赫拉格","萨卡兹雇佣兵A","萨卡兹雇佣兵B","爱国者","阿米娅","萨卡兹雇佣兵","整合运动A","整合运动B","整合运动成员","盾卫"]}